#: ../../dapp-dev-guide/tutorials/upgrade-tutorial.rst:23
msgid ""
"When you first deploy the contract, you must include an *upgrade* "
"function. Since the contract is immutable, you cannot add the *upgrade* "
"function after deployment. Without the this function, you cannot upgrade "
"the contract. In other words, you must include the *upgrade* function "
"when you first deploy the contract."
msgstr ""

